snippet.title: #Video | नथुनिया 2 | Nathuniya 2 | Official Music Video | Khesari Lal Yadav ft. Daisy Shah |New Song
snippet.description:
"नथुनिया" के धमाल के बाद, अब "नथुनिया 2" ले के आ गइल बा बवाल!
ट्रेंडिंग स्टार खेसारी लाल यादव और बॉलीवुड सुपरस्टार डेज़ी शाह के धमाकेदार जोड़ी अब भोजपुरिया अंदाज़ में कर रही बा आगाज़!
"नथुनिया 2" – अब हो चुकल बा रिलीज़! 
देखीं, झूमीं और शेयर करीं — सिर्फ़ @SaregamaHumBhojpuri  पर!

After the superhit "Nathuniya", the storm continues with "Nathuniya 2"!
Get ready for the explosive bhojpuri-style duo of trending star Khesari Lal Yadav and bollywood star Daisy Shah — setting the screen on fire!
"Nathuniya 2" – OUT NOW!
Watch it, vibe to it & share it — only on @SaregamaHumBhojpuri 

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song – Nathuniya 2 
Singer – Khesari Lal Yadav
Featuring – Daisy Shah
Lyrics & Music – Krishna Bedardi 
Composer – KRK Yadav
Music Arranger – VS Chauhan
Director - Sumit Kumar & Rohit Shetty
Choreographer - Rohit Shetty 
DOP - Jason Nambardar
Editor - Nitin FCP
Asst. Director - Pawan Pandey
Asst. Editor - Narendra Jaiswal
2nd Asst. Editor - Siddharth Tiwari
Post Production - Arts For Production 
Colorist - Tapasvi Asija

Lyrics:-

हो अपना अखियां में काजरा लगाके,
रखनी जुड़ा में साड़ी अटकाके,,
आ हमार पावडर क्रीम लागे हो जाई डिम बाटे एकही जगहिया खाली,,
हो सईया बिन नथुनिया के डाली,,

त चोली चिल्लाता ये राजा हो जल्दी आ जा हो,
कमर से साड़ी सरक जाता सीरिया जा हो,,
त करी अईसन सिंगार के 
बिन भतार के,
मन नाही करे रही झार के बिन भतार के,,
त कहे बिंदिया बलम तू सतावल कर कम लाल भईल बा घुसा से ओठलाली हो सईया बिन,,,

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada

snippet.title: World Record YOGA with Saurabh Bothra | International Yoga Day 2025
snippet.description:
Join Free Yoga -  https://habuild.yoga/free
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

You may like these 5 videos:

Daily Exercise for PARENTS under 20-Minutes - https://youtu.be/FP4Z8yRWe6A
Daily Pranayama under 15-Minutes - https://youtu.be/I77hh5I69gA
Daily Core-Strengthening Exercises for Beginners - https://youtu.be/1HegMTiTIDQ
15 Best ANTI-AGING Exercises for Parents - https://youtu.be/B2Ex4M13R04
Effective EYE YOGA for Healthy Eyes! - https://youtu.be/4l85ddf6jrU

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

গভীর শোকের সঙ্গে আমরা জানাচ্ছি কোচ টাইলার ওয়ালের আকস্মিক প্রয়াণের কথা। কোচ ওয়াল ছিলেন একজন অসাধারণ মানুষ, যাঁর দয়া এবং আন্তরিকতা তাঁর পরিচিত সকলের হৃদয়ে ছাপ ফেলেছিল। তাঁর চলে যাওয়া আমাদের হৃদয়ে গভীর বেদনা রেখে গেছে।
এই দুঃখজনক সংবাদ পেয়ে আমরা কোচ ওয়ালের পরিবারের সঙ্গে যোগাযোগ করেছি যে, এই ভিডিওটি শেয়ার করা উচিত কি না। তাদের করুণা ও বিবেকবান মনোভাবের জন্য, তারা জানিয়েছেন টাইলার চাইতেন তাঁর আশাবাদী ও ইতিবাচক বার্তাটি অনেকে পৌঁছিয়ে যাক, এমনকি তাঁর অনুপস্থিতিতেও।

Pokornie prosimy o uszanowanie pamięci trenera Walla i uszanowanie prywatności jego rodziny w tym trudnym czasie.

snippet.title: Iran Launches Revenge Attack After US Strike: Israel Panics Amid Huge Missile Salvo- First In 24 Hrs
snippet.description:
Hours after US bombed Iran's nuclear sites, Tehran launched revenge attacks on Israel, targeting major cities. Sirens rang out in central and northern Israel as a fresh salvo of Iranian missiles was detected by the Israeli military. Iran had warned of consequences if US attacked its nuclear facilities. Watch the video for more details.

snippet.title: Brahmanandam Speech| Kannappa Pre Release Event- Hyderabad | Vishnu Manchu | Prabhas
snippet.description:
Legendary actor and comedy icon Brahmanandam took the stage at the Kannappa Pre-Release Event held at JRC Convention, Hyderabad, delivering a speech filled with humor, wisdom, and warmth.

In his unique style, Brahmanandam shared his excitement about Kannappa, praised the team led by Vishnu Manchu, and entertained the audience with his wit and charm. Don’t miss this delightful moment from the grand event!

🎬 Get ready for the epic release of Kannappa on 27th June 2025 worldwide!

#kannappa  #kannappamovie  #KannappaPreReleaseEvent #prereleaseevent  #hyderabadevent #kannappa27thjune  #brahmanandam #BrahmanandamSpeech

✨ CAST & CREW:

Starring: Vishnu Manchu, Mohan Babu, Prabhas, Mohanlal, Akshay Kumar, Sarat Kumar, Kajal Aggarwal, Arpit Ranka, Brahmanandam, Saptagiri, Mukesh Rishi, Madhubala, Aishwarya Bhaskaran, Brahmaji, Devaraj, Raghu Babu, Siva Balaji, Sampath Ram, Lavi Pajni, Surekha Vani, Preity Mukundhan, Kaushal And Adhurs Raghu.

Story & Screenplay: Vishnu Manchu
Producer: Dr. M. Mohan Babu
Banner: Twenty Four Frames Factory & AVA Entertainment
Director: Mukhesh Kumar Singh
Cinematographer: Sheldon Chau
Music Director: Stephen Devassy
Editor: Anthony Gonsalvez
Production Designer: Chinna
Executive Producer: Vinay Maheshwari & R. Vijay Kumar
Stunts Master: Kecha Khamphakdee
Choreography: Prabhudeva, Brinda & Ganesh
PRO: Haswath Saravanan & Sai Satish
DI & Sound Mixing: Annapurna Studios

Music Label: T-Series

Don’t miss this captivating performance that perfectly matched the spirit of Kannappa, the much-awaited pan-Indian film releasing on 27th June 2025.

snippet.title: Dil Thaam Ke | Maalik | Rajkummar Rao, Huma Qureshi | Sachin-Jigar | Rashmeet K, Rana M, Amitabh B
snippet.description:
Feel the rhythm take over with Dil Thaam Ke — the ultimate dance Song from Maalik! Starring Rajkummar Rao and Huma Qureshi, this high-energy track features electrifying music by Sachin-Jigar, soulful vocals by Rashmeet Kaur & Rana Majumdar, and powerful lyrics penned by Amitabh Bhattacharya.

In Cinemas 11th July 2025

Stay updated with the latest videos from Tips Official. Subscribe on the link below.
http://youtube.com/tipsofficial

Song Details : 
Music - Sachin - Jigar
Singer: Rashmeet Kaur, Rana Majumdar
Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya 
Music Production Head - Romil Ved
Programmed & Arranged:- Abhishek Singh (White Noise Collectives) 
Recording Engineer: Swar Mehta & Susmeet Rewaskar (White Noise Collectives)
Mixed & Mastered: Eric Pillai 
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai

Movie Details : 
Banner: Tips Films Ltd. & Northern Lights Films
Directed By Pulkit
Produced By Kumar Taurani & Jay Shewakramani
Cast: Rajkummar Rao, Prosenjit Chatterjee, Manushi Chhillar, Medha Shankr, Huma Qureshi, Swanand Kirkire 
Director Of Photography: Anuj Rakesh Dhawan
Written By Jyotsana Nath & Pulkit
Production Designer: Rita Ghosh
Costume Designer : Niharika Bhasin
Editor: Zubin Sheikh
Music Composer: Sachin-Jigar
Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya
Background Score: Ketan Sodha
Sound Designer: Anish John
Re-Recording Mixer: Debajit Changmai (Futureworks Media Ltd)
Choreographers: Vijay Ganguly, Shazia S Samji & Piyush Bhagat
Action Director : Vikram Dahiya
Casting Director: Mukesh Chhabra, CSA
DI Colourist: Ashirwad Hadkar
VFX Supervisor: Nitesh Sharma
DI: Prime Focus Ltd.
Publicity Design: Paras Kanani [House Of AWE]
Marketing Director Varun Gupta [Max]
Visual Promotions: Just Right Studioz NX

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Some scientists claim to have captured a strange glowing phenomenon, something like an aura emerging from the human body using their instruments. You might’ve seen viral reports on the internet suggesting this too. But what exactly is this mysterious light that appears in living beings but vanishes after death and that isn’t just body heat?

This very question intrigued a brilliant Japanese scientist, Masaki Kobayashi from Tohoku University, back in 2009. To find the answer, he conducted a groundbreaking experiment on this so-called “human light”. Little did he know, his discovery would shake the way we perceive reality.

Interestingly, many scientists at the time believed no scientific evidence could ever prove the existence of a soul or consciousness and they conducted experiments to support that view. But Masaki wasn’t fully convinced. What did he know about this mysterious light that others didn’t? So, was Masaki Kobayashi just measuring light, or was he witnessing something far deeper?
Is this strange glow just a biological glitch, or the first glimpse of the human soul?
And if something truly leaves the body when we die, what exactly are we?

snippet.title: GAANJI - Official Music Video | Chandan Shetty | Folk x Fusion
snippet.description:
From North Karnataka to the World: A Folk Song Reimagined Through Dance. Having zero expectations and a full heart, I present to you this experimental music video — a piece of art born from a deeply personal journey.

I composed this song nine years ago, inspired by a beloved folk rhyme from North Karnataka. Over time, its melody stayed close to me, quietly asking to be brought to life in a new form.

The visual inspiration comes from a range of minimalistic music videos, especially those shot on white-screen backgrounds (like ‘Sorry’ from Justin Bieber). I finally started working on the video in 2023, and just two months ago, we brought it to life.

We held virtual auditions across India, and with the brilliant support of choreographers Praveen Veigas,  Pushpa, and Muskan, we selected 10 incredible dancers who brought their energy and magic to this performance.

This project would not have been possible without the dedication and brilliance of a phenomenal team:
        •        Co-Producer: Greeshma Gowda
        •        DOP: Suhas Amin
        •        Editor & VFX: Dheeraj Poojary
        •        Programming, Mixing & Mastering: Agastya Raag
        •       Dancers: Alina Khan, Yukta, Muskan, Chaitanya, Payal, Jaquline, Sana, Shivani, Sneha.
        •       Chorus: Mahalakshmi, Harismaran . A, Harshit N.U, Siri B.S, Prerana Navalgi, Nikisha H.A, Sana .S, Meghana Saishree, Shivani .S, Kshama .D Raj, Sanchita Vinay, M. Madhumitha, Dhriti Vishwanath, Isha .V, Omkar Kumble, Ghanashyam G.R, Tanav .S, Arav G.A, Ruchitha .V, Ridhima .K, Pranathi .V, Panvi N.U.
        •      Poster Design : Ankith Anil 
        •      Digitally Distributed by A3 Labels
        •      Digital Promotions: Digital Magnet Media - Dhanu Krishnaa


To all the technicians and artists involved — your work has been outstanding, and I deeply appreciate each one of you.

This video is directed by Chandan Shetty, and represents not just a song, but a dream nurtured over time.

I truly hope you connect with it, feel the spirit behind it, and show it some love.

Listen on your favorite platform: 
Spotify:https://open.spotify.com/track/0nTl1C6WCW2yv5P2G8eK87?si=07abf20415544345
Jio Saavn:https://www.jiosaavn.com/song/gaanji/Oxwgfyd0VXI
Youtube Music:https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=RUtZl_J0uqs&si=i8lDF-NJKb6_S07W
Amazon Music:https://music.amazon.in/tracks/B0FDLBF9XT?marketplaceId=A21TJRUUN4KGV&musicTerritory=IN&ref=dm_sh_HDPV6NH03U4CakUQzl0UUvf2A
iTunes:https://music.apple.com/us/song/gaanji/1821465090
Apple Music:https://music.apple.com/us/song/gaanji/1821465090
Gaana:https://gaana.com/song/gaanji
Instagram:https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1395192328197759/

snippet.title: बचपन का प्यार ढूंढने इंडिया लौटी करीना - Kareena & Tusshar Kapoor ज़बरदस्त सीन - Jeena Sirf Mere Liye
snippet.description:
► Click here to Subscribe the channel : https://bit.ly/3HS054l 

बचपन का प्यार ढूंढने इंडिया लौटी करीना - ज़बरदस्त सीन - Kareena Kapoor, Tusshar Kapoor, Mallika Sherawat - Jeena Sirf Mere Liye 2002 - Blockbuster Movie - Superhit 

The story revolves around Karan and Pooja, two young friends who meet at a picturesque hill station every summer. However, fate intervenes when Pooja’s affluent family relocates, leading to their estrangement. As they
mature, both characters harbour memories of their bond, with Pooja finding solace in her writing and Karan unintentionally caught in a romantic misunderstanding with Seema, played by Mallika Sherawat. A culmination of
misunderstandings, familial pressures, and emotional realisations eventually lead them back to each other, imploring viewers to reflect on the complexities of love and connection.

◾ Film : Jeena Sirf Merre Liye 2002 (जीना सिर्फ मेरे लिये)
◾ Director :- Talat Jani (तलत जानी)
◾ Cast: - Kareena Kapoor (करीना कपूर), Tusshar Kapoor (तुषार कपूर), Kader Khan (कादर खान), Mallika Sherawat (मल्लिका शेरावत), Alok Nath (आलोक नाथ), Himani Shivpuri (हिमानी शिवपुरी), Vijayendra Ghatge
◾ Genre:- Romantic Drama रोमांटिक ड्रामा
◾ Language:- Hindi

#kareenakapoorkhan #tusharkapoor #kaderkhan #malikasherawat #202s #romantic #bollywood #lovemovies #hindimovie #latestmovies #besthindimovies #nostalgia #zarazara #film #hindimovie

snippet.title: Back to Back Comedy Scenes 😍🤣| Kick | Ravi Teja | Brahmanandam | Ilena | Ali | Telugu Comedy Scene
snippet.description:
Kick is a 2009 Indian Telugu-language action comedy film directed by Surender Reddy from a story by Vakkantham Vamsi. The film stars Ravi Teja, Ileana, and Shaam while Brahmanandam plays a supporting role. 

నైనా(ఇలియానా)కి పోలీస్ ఆఫీసర్ కళ్యాణ కృష్ణ(శ్యామ్)కి పెళ్ళి చూపులలో తన ప్రేమ కథని శ్యామ్ కి చెప్తుంది. ఆ కథలో కళ్యాణ్ (రవితేజ) చిన్నప్పటి నుంచీ కిక్..కిక్ అంటూ కలవరిస్తూంటాడు. అందుకుతగ్గట్లుగానే కిక్ ఇవ్వని ఏ పనీ చెయ్యడు...కిక్కు ఇస్తుందంటే ఎటువంటి పని చెయ్యటానికైనా వెనకాడడు..అంతేగాక కిక్ తగ్గిపోతే ఆ పనిలో కొనసాగటానికి ఇష్టపడడు. దాంతో ఏ ఉద్యోగంలోనూ వారం మించి పనిచేయడు. అలాంటి అతని విచిత్ర జీవితంలోకి ప్రతీది పెపఫెక్ట్ గా ఉండాలనుకునే ఇలియానా ప్రవేశిస్తుంది. అతని ఏటిట్యూడ్ చూసి మొదట ఆమె కసురుకున్నా తర్వాత ప్రేమలో పడుతుంది. పడిందే తడువుగా అతన్ని ఏదన్నా ఉద్యోగంలో చేరి సెటిల్ అవ్వమంటుంది.

snippet.description:

Daya purposefully loses the Antakshari so that everyone can sleep, and Jethalal orders dinner for everyone because they all appear to be hungry.  She makes Champaklal and Jethalal proud with this gesture. As the main guest at the Gokuldham Society Anniversary celebration, Taarak extends an invitation to his friend. #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTXtajBo1G2UEa_wE8BVSU7

snippet.title: Sitaare Zameen Par Movie REVIEW | Suraj Kumar
snippet.description:
SITAARE ZAMEEN PAR Review | Aamir Khan & Genelia Return with an Emotional Ride? 

Aamir Khan is back — this time with Sitaare Zameen Par, alongside Genelia D’Souza in a heartfelt drama that explores learning disabilities, redemption, and second chances.
But does the film live up to the emotional weight of Taare Zameen Par or does it fall into the trap of forced sentimentality?

hi.title: KL Rahul और Ben Stokes की सबसे कठिन बैटिंग चुनौती!
hi.description:
बेन स्टोक्स और के.एल. राहुल मिलकर क्रिकेट की अब तक की सबसे चुनौतीपूर्ण बैटिंग चैलेंज का सामना करने वाले हैं! 

आने वाली टेस्ट सीरीज़ से पहले, दोनों को अपनी-अपनी व्यक्तिगत क्रिकेट परीक्षाओं से गुजरना होगा — जहाँ उनकी सटीकता और ताकत की असली परख होगी। 

इसके बाद ही वे एक साथ मिलकर तेज़ तर्रार बॉलिंग मशीनों और तेजी से हिलते लक्ष्यों के खिलाफ एक रोमांचक "बॉस बैटल" में उतरेंगे।

kn.title: ದಿ ಅಲ್ಟಿಮೇಟ್ ಕ್ರಿಕೆಟ್ ಬ್ಯಾಟಿಂಗ್ ಚಾಲೆಂಜ್ (KL Rahul ಮತ್ತು Ben Stokes)
kn.description:
KL Rahul ಮತ್ತು Ben Stokes ಅಂತಿಮ ಕ್ರಿಕೆಟ್ ಬ್ಯಾಟಿಂಗ್ ಸವಾಲನ್ನು ಎದುರಿಸಲು ಒಗ್ಗೂಡುತ್ತಿದ್ದಾರೆ! 


ಟೆಸ್ಟ್ ಸರಣಿಗೆ ಮೊದಲು, ಅವರು ಪ್ರತ್ಯೇಕವಾಗಿ ತಮ್ಮ ಶಕ್ತಿ ಮತ್ತು ನಿಖರತೆಯನ್ನು ಪರೀಕ್ಷಿಸುವ ವೈಯಕ್ತಿಕ ಕ್ರಿಕೆಟ್ ಸವಾಲುಗಳನ್ನು ಜಯಿಸಬೇಕು. 

 

ಈ ನಂತರ, ಅವರು ಸೇರಿ ಟ್ರಿಕ್ಕಿ ಬೌಲಿಂಗ್

snippet.title: Ep 4430 - PRECAP! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता का उल्टा चश्मा
snippet.description:
Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Produced By: Neela Asit Modi, Asit Kumarr Modi

snippet.title: सूजी मूंगदाल फरा नाश्ते के लिए परफेक्ट स्वाद सेहत सादगी नो फ्राई नो झंझट । Steamed Sooji Fara recipe
snippet.description:
तला-भुना छोड़िए,  खाइए ये स्टीम्ड और हेल्दी फरे, बिना झंझट वाला पौष्टिक नाश्ता,पारंपरिक स्वाद, बनाने में एकदम आसान, Sooji Fara Recipe – A Nutritious Start to Your Day,Low-Oil Breakfast – Sooji Fara with Protein-Rich Stuffing
#fara #breakfast #nashtha

Ingredients for Suji Moong Dal Fare
नमक - Salt - 3/4 tsp
तेल - Oil - 1 tbsp
सूजी - Semolina - 1 cup (180 grams)

For Stuffing
मूंग धुली दाल - Moong dhuli dal - 1/2 cup (100 grams)
नमक - Salt - 1/4 tsp
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 tsp, grated
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1/2 tsp, chopped
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1/2 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
लाल मिर्च पाउडर - Red chilli powder - 1/4 tsp
अमचूर पाउडर - Dry mango powder - 1/4 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/4 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp, crushed
हींग - Asafoetida - 1/2 pinch
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 1-2 tbsp


For Frying
तेल - Oil - 1 tbsp
सरसों के दाने - Mustard seeds - 1/4 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/4 tsp
करी पत्ता - Curry leaves 
तिल - Sesame - 1/2 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli 
नमक - Salt

ഇംഗ്ലീഷ് പേസിന് മുന്നിൽ കോട്ട കെട്ടിയും ആക്രമിച്ചു ജയ്സ്വാൾ ബാറ്റ് വീശിയതോടെ ഒരു ഘട്ടത്തിൽ ബാക് ഫുട്ടിലായ ഇന്ത്യയെ ടോപ്പ് ഗിയറിൽ എത്തിച്ചത്. 42 റൺസെടുത്ത കെഎൽ രാഹുൽ കൂടാരം കയറുമ്പോൾ ഇന്ത്യ ഭേദപ്പെട്ട നിലയിലേക്കുള്ള യാത്ര ആരംഭിച്ചിരുന്നു. രാഹുലിനെ ബ്രൈഡൻ കാഴ്സിന്റെ പന്തിൽ ജോ റൂട്ട് ക്യാച്ചെടുത്തു പുറത്താക്കുകയായിരുന്നു. എന്നാൽ മൂന്നാമനായി എത്തിയ സായ് സുദർശൻ റണ്ണൊന്നുമെടുക്കാതെ കൂടാരം കയറിയതോടെയാണ് ഇന്ത്യ ബാക് ഫുട്ടിലായത്.

Kuberaa movie fdfs  response.
Watch Dhanush, Nagarjuna Kuberaa fdfs review.

Presenting Public review of Kuberaa movie. Kuberaa public review is taken from Bangalore FDFS.

Kuberaa is an 2025 Indian social thriller film directed and co-written by Sekhar Kammula. Produced by Suniel Narang and Puskur Rammohan Rao of Amigos Creations, it is simultaneously shot in Telugu, Tamil and Hindi. The film stars Dhanush, Nagarjuna, Rashmika Mandanna, Jim Sarbh and Dalip Tahil. The film has music composed by Devi Sri Prasad, cinematography by Niketh Bommireddy, editing by Karthika Srinivas and production design by Thota Tharani.

Kuberaa released worldwide from today.

The film stars Dhanush, Nagarjuna, Rashmika Mandanna, Jim Sarbh and Dalip Tahil. The film has music composed by Devi Sri Prasad, cinematography by Niketh Bommireddy, editing by Karthika Srinivas and production design by Thota Tharani.

Kuberaa released worldwide from today.
